title: T.I. & Tiny: Friends & Family Hustle
overview: T.I. and Tiny are joined by a roster of friends as they navigate life -- and most importantly, keep family first. While their large blended family is along for the ride, T.I. and Tiny also surround themselves with friends Toya Wright, Reginae Carter, Monica Brown, LeToya Luckett and Tommicus Walker as they share loyalty and love, and support one another in their personal lives and careers.
